{"id":232832107,"title":"#問題 LV city steamer","content":"大家好～\n收到了家人給的新年禮物 \n是LV的city steamer\n\n因為家人在購買時也沒有檢查\n但我個人比較吹毛求疵\n所以想請問大家這樣狀況是否為正常、還可接受的？\n\n1.鎖頭部分左邊刮痕多，但右邊完全沒有。\n左⬇️\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/8cf93cc9-c2d3-47d4-9067-f1c4c3b28f66/1280.jpeg\n右⬇️\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2fd3dfc1-c6db-4b07-947f-b010a07171e0/1280.jpeg\n我是想說雖然使用後有刮痕難免，不過我才剛拿到就發現有痕跡，而且左右對比真的蠻強烈的；我以為會有保護封膜，但也沒有，反而是內部的地方有。（下一點說明）\n抱歉相機比較沒辦法拍出刮痕，但我就是不太能接受左右這個落差😭\n\n2.內裏扣環皮革處是歪掉的\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/3571a1c6-e10f-4aec-bec1-ca1b406a1fa3/1280.jpeg\n很妙的是裡面金屬部分反而是有封膜保護的，但外面卻沒有，讓我有點問號⋯⋯\n重點是皮革歪的讓我也傻眼😭\n\n以上想請問大家\n如果有這樣狀況是還能接受的嗎？\n\n我是預計明天會打電話詢問一下\n但不清楚是不是我太小題大作了\n\n想先詢問看看大家意見\n感激不盡～～🙏","excerpt":"大家好～收到了家人給的新年禮物，是LV的city steamer，因為家人在購買時也沒有檢查，但我個人比較吹毛求疵，所以想請問大家這樣狀況是否為正常、還可接受的？1.鎖頭部分左邊刮痕多，但右邊完全沒有","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"c573dca4-8afd-4c56-8c53-4402ead7bdad","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-05T15:46:55.508Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-05T15:46:55.508Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":6,"tags":[],"topics":["精品","LV","詢問","問題","包包"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"精品","forumAlias":"boutique","school":"中國科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":6}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/8cf93cc9-c2d3-47d4-9067-f1c4c3b28f66/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2fd3dfc1-c6db-4b07-947f-b010a07171e0/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/3571a1c6-e10f-4aec-bec1-ca1b406a1fa3/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"1435966b-739a-432b-be0a-9849932149e0","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/8cf93cc9-c2d3-47d4-9067-f1c4c3b28f66/640.jpeg","normaliz